<p>Weekends and holidays shouldn&#8217;t be time to recover. They should be time to rejoice.</p><p>Burnout cultures exhaust us through the week and force us to recharge during our time off. Healthy cultures provide daily space to refuel.</p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link image2" target="_blank" href="https://www.instagram.com/p/ChU8FcSOOG3/?hl=en" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F8a722cfc-d801-4974-a998-a08ff5f5a0ee_2250x2250.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F8a722cfc-d801-4974-a998-a08ff5f5a0ee_2250x2250.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F8a722cfc-d801-4974-a998-a08ff5f5a0ee_2250x2250.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F8a722cfc-d801-4974-a998-a08ff5f5a0ee_2250x2250.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F8a722cfc-d801-4974-a998-a08ff5f5a0ee_2250x2250.jpeg" width="382" height="382" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/8a722cfc-d801-4974-a998-a08ff5f5a0ee_2250x2250.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:1456,&quot;width&quot;:1456,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:382,&quot;bytes&quot;:157337,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;